Problem Link:
https://leetcode.com/problems/check-if-binary-string-has-at-most-one-segment-of-ones/?envType=daily-question&envId=2026-03-06

Solution:
class Solution {
public:
    bool checkOnesSegment(string s) {
        for(int i = 1; i < s.size(); i++)
        {
            if(s[i] == '1' && s[i-1] == '0')
            {
                return false;
            }
        }
        return true;
    }
};
